formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	The amount of construction cost has been considered on the basis of the information provided by the competent authorities of the Corporation.
2.	As informed by the management, there has been no progress in the work.
3.	Total number of units to be constructed has been assumed to be built up evenly.
4.	As informed by the management, the amount of installments from beneficiaries have been deposited in the general bank account and hence, the same is considered as RECEIVED AMOUNT in Form-3(Annexure).
5.	Based on the certification provided by the concerned department regarding the data received from banks for the amounts of installments received in the general bank account, we have updated the amount of installments received from respective beneficiaries.
6.	If there will be any changes in the data provided, the same will be updated in the next return against the respective beneficiary.
7.	The agreement execution is under process in many of the beneficiaries. As and when it will be executed and verified by us, the same will be reported by us.
